The bladed muspah is a Melee-based creature encountered during Fate of the Gods. Along with the force muspahs and throwing muspahs, you need to defend against these during Mah's Nightmare. After the quest, they can be found in the Cradle on Freneskae, along with the other two types of muspahs. Using Ancient Magicks against the bladed muspah will double your damage. Using the Shard of Zaros will also make these monsters non-aggressive.

Muspah possess 100% accurate attacks.
